            "id": 6009591,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉美股收黑 台積電千元關情怯 量縮震盪守穩月線",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (6) 日受美股四大指數走低影響，早盤小幅開低，隨後一度翻紅，來回震盪近百點，守穩月線大關，市場觀望氣氛濃厚，權值股普遍在平盤附近游走，預計今日成交量僅 2800 億元，較昨日減少。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009591%2Fl%2F8a72bfac62dacff08a72229584a65963.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股開盤〉美股收黑 台積電千元關情怯 量縮震盪守穩月線。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股走勢分歧，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 隨著股價逼近千元，近關情怯，一度跌至 992 元，跌幅約 1%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 則小跌，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 因日前 ETF 成分股調節大幅回檔，今日回彈近 2%，為大盤走勢增溫。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子股廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 因連日漲多，今回檔近 2%，台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 跌幅也近 1%，其他如日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ASX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ASX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ASX-US</a>)、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UMC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UMC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UMC-US</a>) 都在盤上表態。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，昨日大漲相關個股，今日大多走弱，振樺電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8114:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8114\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8114-TW</a>) 重挫跌停，材料 - KY(4785-TW) 也下挫逾半根，昇達科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3491:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3491\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3491-TW</a>)、緯創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3231-TW</a>) 也有 4% 的跌幅。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
